quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,"Ih, gulle$ seg wanda llan itran"
  56,76,"U, tagi, lemmer a ppeéôem, ard tagallit tameqwôaêant"
  56,77,Ar neppa d Leqwôan ukyis
  56,78,di Tezmamt iffren
  56,79,"Ur t pnalen, siwa wid zeddigen"
  56,80,D tarusi s$uô Mass imavalen
  56,81,"S usali agi, amendeô ma a ppiéidem"
  56,82,"S ôôeéq nnwen, kunwi tnekôem"
  56,83,Mara d tawev s agerjum
  56,84,"kunwi, imiren, teppaôoum"
  56,85,"Nekwni, sennig wen, i Neqôeb $uôes, maca, ur twalam ara"
  56,86,Xas ma ur tellim d wid ur nepwalas
  56,87,"erret p id, ma tessawalem tidep"
  56,88,Ma illa seg iqôiben
  56,89,"ihi, abeêri, laâîeô, di leonan n ssuâada"
  56,90,Ma illa seg iyeffusen
  56,91,"i keçç tifrat, seg iyeffusen"
  56,92,Ma illa seg inekkaôen innetlafen
  56,93,axxam is seg waman ippayzagen
  56,94,ad iô$ deg ujajiê
  56,95,"Ayagi, ih, d tidep itebbten"
  56,96,"Sbuccaâ, s ccekôan, isem n Mass ik Ameqwôaêan"
  57,1,"Sbuccuâen, s ccekôan Öebbi, ayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  57,2,"IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; Issidir, Ineqq; u Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  57,3,"D Neppa ay d amezwaru, ay d aneggaru; d ayen d ibanen akked wayen iffren. Neppa Iéôa yal cci"
  57,4,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, Iâannec af usgeld. Iéôa i ikeççmen ar tmurt, akked wayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id ippadren seg igenni, akked wayen ippalin $uôes. Neppa yidwen, anda ma tellam. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txedmem"
  57,5,IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ar Öebbi ara u$alen lumuô
  57,6,"Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren"
  57,7,"Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS! Efket seg wayen i$ef i kwen Irra, degs, d igensas. Wid iumnen segwen, iseddqen, d ameqwôan warraz nnsen"
  57,8,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tuminem ara s Öebbi? Amazan ipnabi kwen a ppamnem s Mass nnwen. Ni$ $uôes nnesba nnwen, ma tellam d lmumnin"
  57,9,"D Neppa id Issadren i umdan iS, issekniyen iberrzen, iwakken a kwen Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat. Ih, Öebbi, fellawen, d Umâin Ipêunun"
  57,10,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tepseddiqem deg ubrid n Öebbi? N Öebbi lweôt n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur taâdilem ara: wid iseddqen uqbel l$elb, u nnu$en, widak, ad aâlayen, nezzeh, sennig wid iseddqen sin $er da, u nnu$en. Iwaââed asen akw Öebbi ûûam. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem"
  57,11,"Win iôevlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad as d Irr s lufa, u ines warraz ukyis"
  57,12,"Asmi ara twaliv lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, teddun tafat nnsen zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen: \"a lxiô nnwen, assa, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen a pwekkôem! D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  57,13,"Ass ideg ixabiten, argaz tameîîut, ad inin i wid iumnen: \"arout a$, a neddem si tafat nnwen\"! A d inin: \"u$alet ar deffir, a d tqelbem tafat\"! Ad yili garasen lêiv, s tebburt. Zdaxel d aêunu, beôôa, zdat es: aâaqeb"
  57,14,"Ad sen d siwlen: \"day ur nella ara yidwen\"? Ad inin: \"ih! Maca, thewwlem iman nnwen, tekkukram, tcukkem, $elvent kwen lemcihwat, armi d iusa lameô n Öebbi. I$elv ikwen af Öebbi, u$ellav"
  57,15,"Assa, ur ipwaîîaf feddu segwen, ne$ seg wid ijehlen. Axxam nnwen d times; d neppat ay d bab nnwen. A tu$alin tucmip"